        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Hotel manager Shen Xi Fan, a workaholic suffering from insomnia and migraines, seeks help from Chinese medicine doctor He Su Ye. Despite her forgetfulness in taking medicine, their interactions grow beyond a doctor-patient relationship when they realize they live in the same community. Both scarred by past love, they slowly open their hearts. As He Su Ye rediscovers love, his dedication to medicine helps Shen Xi Fan find herself and her true\n\nmatch.",
